location.fullValue: Cultus Plan, Lacamas Hills - Huron Collection

data.description: One of a kind completely custom Mascord designed home built by Cascade West in 2013! House was designed for privacy & quiet, good light utilizing the views from every angle. Efficient floor plan with great spatial design to maximize square footage. Designed to be intimate but accommodate large gatherings for parties and holidays. Quality upgrades throughout the home, well maintained. Views and convenience of walking trails, close to nature while providing close and easy access to Hwy 14, I-205, airport, shopping and famous Camas community/schools! Fire Sprinkler system giving you reduced insurance rates. Chefs and bakers can enjoy this large DREAM kitchen including Dacor appliances, cook island w/gas 5 burner cooktop, double ovens, extra prep sink & eating bar. Warm and cozy primary suite on the main level w/extra-long soaking tub, gorgeous tile shower, heated tile floors, W-I closet with built-ins. Bonus room upstairs and den/office downstairs. Exit the kitchen nook through french door and relax on the quite/private covered back patio, watching nature come to you. Easy maintenance landscaping, 2 car oversized garage with picture windows for light. This home has too many upgrades to list. Please call/txt for amenities list and you will definitely want to see this home in person.
